  deactivate server

  Note right of browser: Browser executes the JS code that requests the JSON data to the server.

  browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
  activate server
  server-->>browser: [{content: "This is a single page app diagram", date: "2026-06-24"}]
  deactivate server

  Note right of browser: The JS file handles the submit of new notes to redrawn the page preventing the default behaviour.

